\id TIT Titus in Boko, Ross Jones 2/08 
\h Titu 
\toc1 Titu 
\toc2 Titu 
\toc3 Tit 
\mt1 TITU 
\imt1 Yã́ pↄ́ kú láɛ bee guuↄ 
\ip Tituá Yesudeɛ, ãma Yuda no (Gal 2.1-3). À gↄ̃̀ Pↄlu ìwa ũɛ mɛ́ à zĩ zↄ̃ↄ kɛ̀ Kↄlɛnideↄ ń Pↄluo maakↄ̃ɛ yã́ musu (2Kln 7.6-16). Pↄlu láɛ bee kɛ̃̀ɛ̀ gↄↄ pↄ́ Titupi ku Kɛlɛtiɛ, à Yesude pↄ́ aa kú ísia gũgũnapiwaↄ yã́gɛa'aɛzĩ nàɛ̀ aà ↄzĩ. 
\ip Lápi daalɛaá waaso pↄ́ Pↄlu ìↄ kɛnɛ́ yã́ɛ (1.1-4). Bee gbɛa yã́ pↄ́ a dìlɛ gãli dↄaanaↄnɛɛ (1.5-16). Lɛɛ pla guu à lɛdà Tituwa gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ àlɛ zĩkɛńnↄↄ yã́ musu: Maeziↄ, nↄɛziↄ (à kũ̀ aa yãdada wɛ̃́ndiaↄnɛ), ɛ̀waasoↄ ń zↄↄ (2.1-15). Lɛɛ àaↄ̃ guu à Yesude yãkɛaↄ bↄↄlɛkɛ̀, kɛ́ an kua aaↄ na, aasuli kↄ̃kpaalɛo (3.1-11). Bee gbɛa à lɛdà Tituwa, à fↄkpàmá (3.12-15). 
\ip Lápi kyokɛna a e kɛ́ lápi waaso dɛ Titu yã́ ũ adoo. Yã'ĩa pↄ́ Pↄlu òↄá yã'ĩa pↄ́ ìↄ Yesudeↄ le mↄ̀ↄmↄↄↄɛ: Yesudeↄ yã́ↄ zɛ́kalɛa ń dↄaanaↄ yãkɛaↄ ń Yesudepiↄ yãkɛaↄ. 
\c 1  
\s1 Titu zĩkɛa Kɛlɛti bùsuu 
\p  
\v 1 Ma Pↄlu, Lua zↄ̀blena, Yesu Kilisi zĩna, à ma zĩ mà gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ Lua ń sɛ́ↄ da a zɛ́u, mí tó aa lousisia sĩana dↄ̃,  
\v 2 an wɛ́ iↄ dↄ àizãna pↄ́ Lua a lɛgbɛ̃̀ zadↄ̃ gↄↄ i daalɛozi, Luapi lí ɛɛto sↄ̃o.  
\v 3 Yã́pi bↄ̀ gupuau a gↄↄwa waaso pↄ́ Lua wá Suabana nàmɛɛ ma ↄzĩ guu, lá a dìlɛwa.  
\v 4 Mámɛ ma láɛ bee kɛ̃̀nɛ Titu,\f + \fr 1.4 \ft 2Kln 8.23\f* ma nɛ'ia Yesu zɛ́ pↄ́ wá kúu sãnu guu. Mae Lua ń Kilisi Yesu wá Suabanapio gbɛ̃kɛkɛnɛ, aai n gba aafia. 
\p  
\v 5 Ma n to Kɛlɛti kɛ́ ǹ yã́ pↄ́ gↄ̃̀ weↄ gↄ̃́gↄ̃, ní gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄ dilɛ wɛ̃́lɛ ń wɛ̃́lɛo lá má ònɛwa.  
\v 6 A maa gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ líↄ ku tàaesai nↄmɛndode ũɛ. Aà nɛ́ↄ ìↄ luayãmanaↄ ũ, i kɛ aaↄ dɛ nɛ́ zazaa lalasideↄ ũ no.  
\v 7 Lá dↄaanaá ziiaɛ Lua zĩ guu, a maa aàↄ dɛ tàaede ge swã́gbãade ge pↄkũmade ge igbɛ̃na ge ãiapãsĩde ge ↄwɛɛlɛmbɛ̃ɛ ũo,  
\v 8 sema nibↄfↄ̃na ũ, laaide pↄ́ zɛ̀ ń maakɛao ũ, gbɛ̃maa pↄ́ a kua adoa mɛ́ a azĩa kũa dↄ̃ ũ,\f + \fr 1.8 \ft 1Tim 3.2-5\f* 
\v 9 gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ zɛ̀ súsu ń Lua yã́ náaideo lá wì danɛ́wa ũ, kɛ́ à e lɛda gbɛ̃pãleↄwa ń yã́ sĩandepio, i gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ bↄ̀ a yã́ kpɛↄ ɛɛkanɛ́ ń ↄzĩ. 
\p  
\v 10 Asa swã́yãmansaide pↄ́ aaì gbɛ̃́ↄ liaa ń ń yã'oaoↄ dasi, atɛ̃sa Yudaↄ guu.  
\v 11 Aaì ua bṹu gbɛ̃́ↄ ↄ̃̀ↄkpa. A maa wà lɛsↄkpanɛ́. Aaì yã́ pↄ́ dɛ wà danɛ́o danɛ́ ↄbɛ̃ɛ'ea yã́i.  
\v 12 Kɛlɛti bùsu ãnabie mɛ̀ Kɛlɛtiↄá ɛɛdeↄnɛ, wài pãsĩↄnɛ, ye'uiade pↄewonsaiↄnɛ.  
\v 13 Yã́piá sĩanaɛ. Ayãmɛto lɛdamá pãsĩpãsĩ, kɛ́ aa zɛ́sɛ súsu.  
\v 14 Aasu laaidↄ Yudaↄ fĩwao ge gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ kɛ̃̀ sĩanawaↄ yãdilɛaↄ.  
\v 15 Pↄe líↄ gbãsĩ gbãsĩsaideↄnɛo, mɛ́ pↄe líↄ gbãsĩsai luayãdansai gbãsĩdeↄnɛo, kɛ́ an làasoo ń ń nↄ̀sɛo vãi yã́i.  
\v 16 Aaì mɛ wa Lua dↄ̃, ↄ̃ an yãkɛa ì ń ɛɛbo. Lua ginzideↄnɛ, aali aà yãmao, aali fↄ̃ yãmaae kɛ̀o. 
\c 2  
\s1 Lɛdaa Lua gbɛ̃́ↄwa 
\p  
\v 1 Mpi sↄ̃, yã́ pↄ́ ì kpaaĩ ń yã́ sĩande daanɛ́o onɛ́.  
\v 2 O maezↄ̃ↄↄnɛ aaↄ ńzĩa kũa dↄ̃ gbɛ̃́ gbiaↄ ũ, laaideↄ ũ. Aa zɛ́sɛ súsu ń yea gbɛ̃́ↄzio ń mɛnao.  
\v 3 O nↄɛzↄ̃ↄↄnɛ lↄ aaↄ ku Lua gbɛ̃́ↄ kuawa. Aasu wàↄ dɛ gudɛna ge vɛ̃ɛ zↄ ũo. Aali yãmaa da nↄgbãaↄnɛ,  
\v 4 aali lɛdamá an baade àↄ ye a zã́zi ń a nɛ́ↄ,  
\v 5 aaↄ dɛ laaideↄ ũ gbãsĩsai, aa laaidↄ ń nↄzãekɛzĩwa, an baade misiilɛ a zã́ɛ, kɛ́ wasu Lua yã́ bɛ̃̀ɛboo yã́i. 
\p  
\v 6 Lɛda ɛ̀waasoↄwa lↄ aaↄ laai vĩ yã́pii guu,  
\v 7 ní maakɛa zɛ́ ↄlↄnɛ́. N yãdaanɛ́ àↄ gbia kolesai.  
\v 8 Yã́zɛde pↄ́ wa fↄ̃ a ɛɛboo danɛ́, wí i gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ bↄ̀ n kpɛ kṹ, kɛ́ i e vãi ò n yã́ musuo yã́i. 
\p  
\v 9 Lɛda zↄↄwa aali misiilɛ ń diiↄnɛ yã́pii guu, aali yã́ pↄ́ a káńgu kɛ. Aasuli bↄ ń yã́ kpɛo.  
\v 10 Aasu ń kpã́i'oo. Aa to aaↄ ń dↄ̃ gbɛ̃́ náaideↄ ũ maamaa, kɛ́ Lua wá Suabana yã́ pↄ́ wi danɛ́ e tɛkɛ yã́pii guu. 
\p  
\v 11 Asa Lua gbɛ̃kɛ pↄ́ mↄ̀ ń gbɛ̃́pii suabaao bↄ̀ gupuau.  
\v 12 Gbɛ̃kɛpi lɛ́ dawɛ̃ɛ wà mikɛ̃ yã́ pↄ́ i kpaaĩ ń Lua yã́ooɛ ń dṹnia pↄnidɛaↄ, wíↄ wázĩa kũa dↄ̃ gbɛ̃maaↄ ũ, luayãmanaↄ ũ dṹnia tiaɛ bee guu,  
\v 13 wíↄ wɛdↄ pↄnakɛgↄↄ pↄ́ wálɛ dã́i. Ɔ̃mɛ wá Lua zↄ̃ↄ wá Suabana Yesu Kilisi mↄgↄↄ gawide ũ.  
\v 14 À azĩa kpà wá gɛ̃ɛ ũ, kɛ́ à wá bↄ vãi píi guu, i wá gbãsĩ wolo a gbɛ̃́ yenzideↄ ũ, gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ maakɛa ãia vĩↄ ũ.  
\v 15 Yã́piↄ onɛ́, ní lɛdaomá, ní ń gba laai ń n ikoo píi. Ńsu to gbɛ̃e sakanguo. 
\c 3  
\s1 Wà laaidↄ maakɛawa 
\p  
\v 1 Dↄ n gbɛ̃́ↄgu aali misiilɛ gbãadeↄnɛ ń ikodeↄ,\f + \fr 3.1 \ft Lom 13.1-2, 1Piɛ 2.13\f* aa ń yãma, aaↄ kú ń maakɛa píi sↄuo.  
\v 2 Aasu gbɛ̃e tↄbɛ̃ɛsio. Aaↄ dɛ nↄ̀sɛdoũde yãkelesaide pↄ́ busaa gbɛ̃́piiɛↄ ũ.  
\v 3 Asa wápiↄ sↄ̃ wá faa vĩ yãao, luayãdansaiↄn wá ũ. Wá sã́sãa, wá dɛ pↄnakɛa ń dↄ́ɛ'ĩi píio zↄↄ ũ. Wiↄ ku nↄ̀sɛvãi ń wɛdↄakↄ̃ɛo guu. Wá dɛ gbɛ̃́ giaↄ ũ, wá zakↄ̃u.  
\v 4 Kɛ́ Lua wá Suabana gbɛ̃kɛ ń aà yea gbɛ̃́ↄzio bↄ̀ gupuau,  
\v 5 ↄ̃ à wá suabà. I kɛ wá maakɛa yã́i no, kɛ́ à wɛ̃nadↄ̃̀wɛ̃ɛ yã́iɛ.\f + \fr 3.5 \ft Ɛfɛ 2.8\f* À wá zu'ò, à wá í dafu, a tò wa gↄ̃ gbɛ̃́ dafuↄ ũ ń a Nisĩna  
\v 6 pↄ́ a pìsiwá gbãao Yesu Kilisi wá Suabana sabai,  
\v 7 ↄ̃ yã́ bↄ̀wanↄ na aà gbɛ̃kɛ yã́i, wa gↄ̃ aà gbablenaↄ ũ, ↄ̃ wá wɛ́ dↄ àizãnai.  
\v 8 Yã́piá sĩanaɛ. 
\p Má ye ǹ kã́asikɛ yã́piↄwa maamaa, kɛ́ luayãmanaↄ e wà mɛkpa maakɛawa. Bee maa, a kã́fĩa vĩ gbɛ̃́ↄnɛ.  
\v 9 Pãalɛ yã́ mìsai gwaaɛ ń deziↄ tↄ́ kↄ̃nwɛao ń sòleo ń lɛkpaakɛa Mↄizi ikoyã musuo, asa yãpãↄnɛ, aa kã́fĩa vĩo.  
\v 10 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ì to wà kɛ̃aa gba laai baa gɛ̃n pla, ní gbasa ǹ aà yá.\f + \fr 3.10 \ft Mat 18.15-17\f* 
\v 11 Ǹyↄ̃ dↄ̃ kɛ́ gbɛ̃́ bee taa ↄ̃̀ↄkpà. Duunkɛnaɛ, à azĩa dàyãu. 
\p  
\v 12 Tó ma Aatema ge Tisiki zĩ̀ma, zɛwɛɛlɛ mↄ ǹ ma le Nikↄpↄli, asa ma zɛò mà buziɛble weɛ.  
\v 13 Kↄai kɛ ǹ zɛ́ kũ̀sũa kɛ bùsu ikoyãdↄ̃na Zenasiɛ ń Apolooo, kɛ́ pↄe su kɛ̃́sãmáo.  
\v 14 A maa wá gbɛ̃́ↄ maakɛa dada, aaiↄ kɛ, aai bↄↄlɛ zɛazɛaↄ kɛ, kɛ́ aasu wàↄ ku pão.  
\v 15 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ wá sãnuↄ fↄkpàma píi. Fↄkpa gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa yewázi Yesu zɛ́ guuↄwa. Lua gbɛ̃kɛkɛɛ́ ápii.